Class IgnoreNewElementsOrderingPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.oxm.documentpreservation.NodeOrderingPolicy
      • org.eclipse.persistence.oxm.documentpreservation.IgnoreNewElementsOrderingPolicy

  • public class IgnoreNewElementsOrderingPolicy
extends NodeOrderingPolicy
    INTERNAL:

    Purpose:An implementation of NodeOrderingPolicy that ignores any new elements when updating a cached document. This is used for the JAXB 2.0 Binder implementation.

    See Also:
    NodeOrderingPolicy
